Package rocks.gioac96.veronica.routing

Class Router<Q extends Request,​S extends Response>

java.lang.Object
Router<Q,​S>
public final class Router<Q extends Request,​S extends Response>
extends java.lang.Object
Application router, responsible for routing Request to a specific Route, that handles the request and generates a response. Builder is extensible with lombok's lombok.experimental.SuperBuilder.
